    crc16-modbus
    Modbus RTU serial protocol
    Width:   16 bits (2 bytes)
    Poly:    0x8005
    Init:    0xFFFF
    RefIn:   True
    RefOut:  True
    XorOut:  0x0000
    Check:   0x4B37  (CRC of '123456789')
    Spec:    CRC:crc16-modbus_le  or  CRC:crc16-modbus_be
